I will join the [https://cs.uwaterloo.ca/ Cheriton School of Computer Science] as an Assistant Professor at the [https://uwaterloo.ca/ Univeristy of Waterloo]. I am looking for PhD and MSc students who are interested in algorithm and complexity of database theory. If you are interested, please send me an email and select me as a potential supervisor in your [https://cs.uwaterloo.ca/future-graduate-students/applying-admissions application].

== Research Interest
Massively parallel query processing, dynamic query processing, oblivious query processing, and machine learning in query optimization.

