== Bio
I was a Visiting Faculty Scholar in the Discrete Algorithm Group at [https://ai.google/research/ Google Research] and worked with [https://pasin30055.github.io/ Pasin Manurangsi], [https://sites.google.com/view/badihghazi/home/ Badih Ghazi] and [https://sites.google.com/site/ravik53/ Ravi Kumar]. Before that, I was a postdoctoral associate within the [https://www.cs.duke.edu/ Department of Computer Science] at [https://www.duke.edu/ Duke University], co-supervised by [https://users.cs.duke.edu/~pankaj/ Prof. Pankaj Agarwal] and [https://users.cs.duke.edu/~junyang/ Prof. Jun Yang]. I received my Ph.D. from the [https://www.cse.ust.hk/ Department of Computer Science and Technology] at [https://www.ust.hk/ HKUST] in August 2019, under the supervision of [https://www.cse.ust.hk/~yike/ Prof. Ke Yi]. During Feb 2019 to May 2019, I was a visiting scholar in the [https://www.cs.wisc.edu/ Department of Computer Sciences] at the [https://www.wisc.edu/ University of Wisconsin Madison] and worked with [http://pages.cs.wisc.edu/~paris/ Paris Koutris]. Prior to that, I received my Bachelor Degree of Engineering from the [http://www.thss.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/soften/index.html School of Software] at [http://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/newthuen/index.html Tsinghua University] in 2014.
